title: #92Noon! Morse/Falvey/Leber/Korzo/Baratz
description: Missing baseball! Opened show with a cold-call to Dustin Morse, then spoke with PBO Derek Falvey to end first hour, Leber in studio midway thru, checked in with the Korzo Kovenant, and ended the show with NFL agent and friend Blake Baratz!
